name: The Aylesbury Occasional Table
description: British artisans are the connoisseurs when it comes to quality, make no exception with the tall intricately designed graceful Aylesbury Occasional Table. Available in any of DAVIDSON's exquisite finishes with an impressive radial pattern to the round tabletop, the Aylesbury is certain to complete a living room where there is the need for a stylish side table. The circular top sits on a subtop supported by four elegantly tapered slender legs, standing on a circular base with a smart collar and protruding feet in gleaming polished nickel.
